ntendo-switch-app-end-support&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23940753/twitch-nintendo-switch-app-end-support" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/31/23940753/twitch-nintendo-switch-app-end-support</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-31T14:20:06-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-31T14:20:06-04:00</updated><title> Apple “Scary Fast” Mac 发布会：4 个最重大的公告</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克的图片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/QYGVdXqLEnKFdubGg_bFlxRGmKc=/52x0:3292x2160/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/72811893/image__4_.0.png&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;9nczWR&quot;>;Apple 的“&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/30 /23933672/apple-event-mac-october-news-updates-products-scary-fast&quot;>;可怕的快&lt;/a>;”展示已经结束。在发布会期间，Apple 揭开了一些配备了该公司最新版本内部芯片的全新 Mac 的面纱。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;44qUJz&quot;>;如果您对所有内容感到好奇关于新产品，以下是此次活动的主要公告摘要。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;yDQjuQ&quot;>; &lt;!-- ######## 开始批量视频 ######## -->;&lt;div data-analytics-viewport=&quot;video&quot; data-analytics-action=&quot;volume:view:article:middle&quot; data-analytics-label=&quot;M3|114083&quot; data-volume-uuid=&quot;7f233f3c8&quot; 数据-volume-id=&quot;114083&quot; data-analytics-placement=&quot;article:middle&quot; data-volume-placement=&quot;article&quot; data-volume-autoplay=&quot;false&quot; id=&quot;volume-placement-626&quot; class=&quot;volume -video&quot; data-volume-player-choice=&quot;youtube&quot;>;&lt;/div>; &lt;!-- ######## 视频结束音量 ######## -->; &lt;/div>; &lt; h2 id=&quot;Sx2KDq&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/30/23938676/apple-m3-chip-gpu-upgrade-hardware-accelerated-ray-tracing-gaming- Specs-release-date&quot;>;更强大的 M3 芯片系列&lt;/a>;&lt;/h2>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：Apple&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id= &quot;53rqhO&quot